          text: "<p>&gt; I urge all the ‘let’s move to GItLab or other’ people give that a hard thought and how that will eventually expire.</p><p>Either they eventually fail&#x2F;become evil, or they don&#x27;t. If they do, just move somewhere else. If they don&#x27;t, good.</p><p>(Benefits of non-proprietary software and standards like git.)</p>",
