          url: null,
          text: '<p>GitLab took external investments will have a liquidity event at some point. That means an acquisition or an IPO. Right now we&#x27;re aiming for an IPO <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;about.gitlab.com&#x2F;strategy&#x2F;#goals" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;about.gitlab.com&#x2F;strategy&#x2F;#goals</a> as we have since 2015 when we took the first external investment.</p>',
