      type: "comment",
      author: "EchelonFuxMe",
      title: null,
      url: null,
      text: "<p>Speaking of fickle developers, I&#x27;m already planning my exit.</p><p>Any mention of Microsoft is enough to turn me off, I have seen enough - I have had enough.</p>",
      points: null,
      parent_id: 17221527,
