                  text: "<p>I couldn&#x27;t agree more. What a pain. GitHub good bye, hello GitLab (I already am on Bitbucket).</p><p>Currently, Microsoft is blocking an open source mod of the Halo Online engine, called ElDewrito. It&#x27;s an incredibly fun to play mod but now development has been halted because of legal action. I hate Microsoft for all the things you mentioned.</p>",
