                          url: null,
                          text: "<p>If GitHub does get sold to MS and I end up moving to GitLab, I&#x27;ll probably push one last commit to the GitHub repo adding a header saying the project has moved, with a link to the GitLab repo. It&#x27;s not perfect, but it wouldn&#x27;t be too bad.</p>",
