                              text: "<p>Until MSFT&#x2F;GitHub does what Sourceforge.net did - taking over project sites from projects which moved away and adding malware (adware&#x2F;spyware) into those ;)</p><p>(I believe with all critique on Microsoft they aren&#x27;t as bad, but want to exemplarize the risk)</p>",
