      text: "<p>Heck, I already prefer Gitlab and&#x2F;or Bitbucket because they let me run free (or at least self-hosted in Gitlab&#x27;s case, not sure what their hosted option&#x27;s like) private repos. Github&#x27;s just got the mindshare going for it. But maybe now that&#x27;ll change.</p>",
