              url: null,
              text: "<p>I expect it&#x27;ll happen to Gitlab at some point, but the beauty of self-hosted is that I can cut ties with the organization and continue using their software anyway because it&#x27;s entirely running on my machine.</p><p>Which, incidentally, is just one reason I usually strongly prefer self-hosted options over SaaS. You&#x27;re not signing a pact to become beholden to the business whims of a third party.</p>",
