          text: "<p>Gitlab also lets you register private gitlab-runners on gitlab.com, which is a killer feature for running CI on setups that aren&#x27;t plain docker-in-the-cloud (such as integration-testing apps that require resources on our LAN, or macOS&#x2F;iOS builds with private keychain items that is much easier to configure on a local Mac). (A side bonus is that you don&#x27;t even have to pay for any CI &quot;minutes&quot;)</p>",
