              type: "comment",
              author: "Symbiote",
              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: '<p>&gt; your data is sold</p><p>It&#x27;s now easier to see some of this, with the GDPR rules.</p><p>The Gitlab cookie page lists 80 &quot;marketing&quot; cookies which may be set: <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;about.gitlab.com&#x2F;privacy&#x2F;cookies&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;about.gitlab.com&#x2F;privacy&#x2F;cookies&#x2F;</a></p>',
