                  type: "comment",
                  author: "phs318u",
                  title: null,
                  url: null,
                  text: "<p>Wow. On the one hand I&#x27;m impressed with the openness (almost - what does purpose=&#x27;unclassified&#x27; mean?), as well as the option to elect which cookie category I agree to. On the other hand... my, that&#x27;s a lot of tracking!</p>",
