              type: "comment",
              author: "caf",
              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p><i>...the other paid accounts, which therefore must be uncompetitively priced,...</i></p><p>That doesn&#x27;t follow.  If the paid accounts are selling, then they must be priced appropriately relative to their competition and the value they provide.  The cost doesn&#x27;t factor into it - and free accounts are just a marketing cost, like putting up a billboard.</p>",
