                  created_at_i: 1528074764,
                  type: "comment",
                  author: "yrashk",
                  title: null,
                  url: null,
                  text: '<p>With tools like SIT (<a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sit.fyi" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sit.fyi</a>) you can keep your issues and patches inside of the Git (or other SCM) repository.</p>',
