                          type: "comment",
                          author: "yrashk",
                          title: null,
                          url: null,
                          text: "<p>Yes, Pagure is also a great project!</p><p>At my level of understanding it, the main difference between Pague and SIT is that SIT&#x27;s story is more about decentralization (and SIT also provides its core to other potential applications beyond software development niche)</p>",
