              type: "comment",
              author: "brownbat",
              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p>Hmm, of those, if I could specify &quot;pick one of these 20 DNS resolvers at random for each query&quot; I might...</p><p>Sorry, tangential thought, I agree with your main point, and the others are much tougher.</p>",
