              text: '<p>(shameless plug) I recently built a tool (SIT, <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sit.fyi" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sit.fyi</a>) that has decentralizes issue tracking and similar workflows, giving full days ownership and independence of storage and transport. Can be (and actively being) used with Git, or other SCMs.</p>',
