          type: "comment",
          author: "acidburnNSA",
          title: null,
          url: null,
          text: "<p>Good point. It&#x27;s not too crazy to have people behind major open-source efforts get their own VPS&#x27;s and run Phabricator or Gitlab. With a universal login akin to OAuth maybe it&#x27;s doable.</p>",
          points: null,
