                      type: "comment",
                      author: "stevekemp",
                      title: null,
                      url: null,
                      text: "<p>Funny you say that, as 1999 was the year that SourceForge was launched.</p><p>Back in the day that was the centralised site that people used to host code, mailing-lists, issues, and etc.</p>",
                      points: null,
                      parent_id: 17222591,
