          text: "<p>&gt;Maybe this event will finally shift things back into a decentralized direction.</p><p>Absolutely no chance, and I&#x27;m fine with that. Sorry, but I don&#x27;t feel like spinning up a slhit server and managing all that goes along with it. I just want my code hosted somewhere that others can access. These meta issues are just noise and don&#x27;t bother me (or 95%+ of the people using GH) one bit.</p>",
