          text: "<p>I think the network effect is too great to ignore. I would guess the number of potential contributors you get just by using GitHub, where many people have an account and know the workflow&#x2F;UI, is bigger than any other place.</p><p>5 years from now when GitLab is acquired by Google we&#x27;ll have to migrate again.</p>",
