                      created_at_i: 1528067009,
                      type: "comment",
                      author: "rurban",
                      title: null,
                      url: null,
                      text: "<p>But how do you transport your issues and CI integration and deployment? The googlecode to github transport was already a desaster.\nCode is easy, it&#x27;s the rest which has the value.</p>",
                      points: null,
                      parent_id: 17222628,
