                          created_at_i: 1528073864,
                          type: "comment",
                          author: "gsich",
                          title: null,
                          url: null,
                          text: '<p><a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;developer.github.com&#x2F;v3&#x2F;issues&#x2F;#list-issues" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;developer.github.com&#x2F;v3&#x2F;issues&#x2F;#list-issues</a> then reimport it with whatever your target system provides.</p><p>Edit your CI scripts. Your CI should not be dependent on Github to work, besides maybe pulling code from it. But then it&#x27;s just a simple change.</p>',
                          points: null,
                          parent_id: 17222941,
