      text: "<p><i>As [Microsoft CEO Satya] Nadella increasingly moves the company away from complete dependence on the Windows operating system to more in-house development on Linux, the company needs new ways to connect with the broader developer community.</i></p><p>If you told me ten years ago that someday Microsoft would buy GitHub as part of its strategy to do &quot;more in-house development on Linux&quot;, I&#x27;d have assumed the acquisition was announced on April 1.</p>",
