      created_at_i: 1528059630,
      type: "comment",
      author: "atlasM",
      title: null,
      url: null,
      text: "<p>Funnily enough a friend of mine and I migrated some of our projects over to GitLab right before this original story broke. It’s really unfortunate though that this will probably go through since GitHub was&#x2F;is really the staple site for social programming and project management, something that GitLab is certainly lacking.</p>",
