      title: null,
      url: null,
      text: "<p>Perhaps there is a market for a really simple Git based issue tracker, which doesn’t require Ruby. This acquisition feels like Freshmeat &#x2F; SourceForge v2; the hardcore OSS enthusiasts will begin their exodus.\nIs there an argument for actually building simple issues management into Git itself with a simple API for pull requests?</p>",
