      text: "<p>It was good while it lasted.</p><p>We will have to start migrating our software there into a more neutral platform.</p><p>I don&#x27;t like the consolidation in Software in which there are only 5-6 huge players. It means politics and private interest of the conglomerate take precedence over everything else, like competence, and freedom.</p><p>Those oligopolies can just send their lawyers against competition or just buy them to stop the threat.</p>",
