      text: '<p>Gitlab is seeing 10x the normal daily amount of repositories</p><p><a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;gitlab&#x2F;status&#x2F;1003409836170547200?s=19" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;gitlab&#x2F;status&#x2F;1003409836170547200?s=19</a></p>',
