          author: "ajmurmann",
          title: null,
          url: null,
          text: "<p>That&#x27;s assuming people here care deeply about open source and it&#x27;s philosophy. It&#x27;s probably fair to say that most people on HN care a lot more about how building the next Atlassian or GitHub and conveniently being able to use OSS for that than about those philosophical values.</p>",
