              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p>Well, clearcase is a horrible monster and it would benefit just about everyone on Earth if it dies.</p><p>How many drivers on the road would be less likely to cut someone off or road rage if they didn&#x27;t have to deal with ClearCase again?  I&#x27;m sure that number is greater than zero.</p><p>I&#x27;m only being partially facetious.  ClearCase truly is the worst.</p>",
