                  text: "<p>Xcode is the successor to Project Builder, the development environment for NeXT. It is written in Objective-C and AppKit.</p><p>Xcode was designed for writing Mac apps, why would anyone want to write Mac apps on a PC, when they&#x27;d need a Mac to test them anyway?</p><p>It&#x27;s only after the iPhone that the question of a <i>port</i> to other platforms has arisen. But that would be a huge task equivalent to a full rewrite. Even Apple doesn&#x27;t have the resources to pull that off smoothly.</p>",
