                          url: null,
                          text: "<p>I still use Wunderlist and probably will until they forcefully shut it down. Tried the ToDo app, and I don&#x27;t get why they basically tried to rewrite Wunderlist. The ToDo app was so buggy and crashed all the time not to mention it&#x27;s lack of features. Hopefully Microsoft learns from this mistake of trying to do a crappy useless rewrite.</p>",
