                              title: null,
                              url: null,
                              text: "<p>&gt; Meanwhile, I&#x27;d really like for people to stop hating Microsoft just because &quot;Microsoft&quot;</p><p>Why is that? Why should people forget how evil MS was and still is?</p>",
