                                  author: "intended",
                                  title: null,
                                  url: null,
                                  text: "<p>The call is not to forget - I didn’t see that from the comment.</p><p>However knee jerk responses are today out of line with MSFTs behavior and actual ability.</p><p>Simply they are anti-objective and inefficient in discussing current reality.</p>",
