                                              type: "comment",
                                              author: "eli",
                                              title: null,
                                              url: null,
                                              text: '<p>I&#x27;m not personally concerned but some big companies definitely are <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.retaildive.com&#x2F;news&#x2F;report-target-opts-out-of-amazon-cloud-services&#x2F;503885&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.retaildive.com&#x2F;news&#x2F;report-target-opts-out-of-am...</a></p>',
