                                                    "2018-06-04T07:50:19.000Z",
                                                  created_at_i: 1528098619,
                                                  type: "comment",
                                                  author: "laumars",
                                                  title: null,
                                                  url: null,
                                                  text: "<p>Gnome is open source though so Microsoft wouldn&#x27;t need to buy the hosting provider to read it&#x27;s source.</p><p>To be honest, even with regards to private repos, I can&#x27;t see Microsoft reading the source code because that would be a massive law case waiting to happen. What I&#x27;m more concerned about is Microsoft trying to integrate more of their own suite into Github. I&#x27;m also concerned about the future of Atom; which I specifically chose over VSC because it wasn&#x27;t managed by Microsoft.</p>",
                                                  points: null,
