                                                          author: "laumars",
                                                          title: null,
                                                          url: null,
                                                          text: "<p>I already self-host personal projects but that is only part of the story since I cannot (and should not) dictate what solutions other people use. A pretty significant proportion of open source projects I have contributed to have been Github hosted so even if I don&#x27;t use it for personal projects I still will need to use it if I want to continue to contribute to those other projects.</p>",
