                                      title: null,
                                      url: null,
                                      text: "<p>Do you have examples of Microsoft acquiring technology that was beloved and embraced by it&#x27;s community and making it better?</p><p>MGS did right by Bungie&#x2F;Halo circa XBox; though Halo hadn&#x27;t yet been released, and it&#x27;s initial fanbase were all Marathon fans.</p>",
