                                              url: null,
                                              text: "<p>Minecraft was going in the toilet slowly far before Microsoft acquired them, but the changes they made have not been for the better in my opinion. Xamarin was plainly bad before acquisition, and as far as I&#x27;ve been able to discern this hasn&#x27;t changed.</p>",
