                                      created_at: "2018-06-04T04:27:17.000Z",
                                      created_at_i: 1528086437,
                                      type: "comment",
                                      author: "__jack_rabbit__",
                                      title: null,
                                      url: null,
                                      text: "<p>I&#x27;m not really interested in being part of a &quot;healthy discussion&quot; with Microsoft. There are enough people telling Microsoft about all the things it is doing to make people dislike it.</p><p>It knows what these things are. If it wants to stop doing them, then I&#x27;m happy to use some of its products. Until then, I&#x27;m going to gitlab now, because Microsoft sucks!</p>",
