                                          type: "comment",
                                          author: "sime2009",
                                          title: null,
                                          url: null,
                                          text: "<p>Codeplex died because GitHub won. There was little point in keeping Codeplex around especially after MS decided to move their open source stuff to where the developers were, i.e. GitHub.</p>",
                                          points: null,
