                                      created_at_i: 1528090609,
                                      type: "comment",
                                      author: "feanaro",
                                      title: null,
                                      url: null,
                                      text: "<p>&gt; I&#x27;m not asking for that, but making wild baseless predictions of how the service will go to shitter or how suddenly all private code will be ripped off and &quot;I&#x27;m going to gitlab now, because Microsoft sucks!&quot; is not part of a healthy discussion.</p><p>But they&#x27;re not <i>baseless</i> predictions, they&#x27;re based on past information and it tells us it would be prudent to minimize reliance of Github sooner rather than later.</p>",
                                      points: null,
