                                  created_at_i: 1528082220,
                                  type: "comment",
                                  author: "macspoofing",
                                  title: null,
                                  url: null,
                                  text: "<p>Because Microsoft was never that evil and they aren&#x27;t evil today. It took me seeing the stuff Apple got away with the iPhone to see what a non-issue Microsoft 90s desktop hegemony was. The fear was overblown.</p>",
