                              created_at_i: 1528107439,
                              type: "comment",
                              author: "Konryan",
                              title: null,
                              url: null,
                              text: "<p>People hate Microsoft for &quot;being Microsoft&quot; BECAUSE of what Microsoft is, does and has done.</p><p>I&#x27;m sure you will find most people who voice those opinions have their own reasons, based on history, to be distrustful of Microsoft and the way this acquisition will be handled.</p>",
