                                          url: null,
                                          text: "<p>IE is abandoned, isn&#x27;t it? Keep in mind that Microsoft bought Andreessens code from NCSA after Andreessen left to found Netscape, so Netscape was competing against a bad version of itself, made worse by Microsoft.</p>",
