                              text: '<p>Haloween documents, and literally the twenty years they&#x27;ve been trying to destroy free software.</p><p>Not to mention . . :</p><p><a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;jamiebuilds&#x2F;status&#x2F;1002696910266773505" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;twitter.com&#x2F;jamiebuilds&#x2F;status&#x2F;1002696910266773505</a></p><p>Tl;dr, Microsoft ignored his license, attributed nothing, and copied his program directory-by-directory.</p><p>Fuck Microsoft. Trust them with email, not your software.</p>',
