                                      text: "<p>Mod parent up.\nI bought a Surface Pro thinking I should give Windows 10 Pro a chance with WSL on it. Even the “Pro” version comes with bubble gum jam games on it, ads, spyware &#x2F; telemetry and the like. No way of removing it.\nI wiped Windows 10 after a week and installed Ubuntu.</p>",
