                                          title: null,
                                          url: null,
                                          text: "<p>Off topic, but how is the experience with Ubuntu on the surface. I love the hardware and the pen of the surface pro, but Xubuntu has been my daily driver for a few years now, and I can&#x27;t imagine going back to Windows.</p><p>My main requirement is for a good experience with the pen...</p>",
