                                              url: null,
                                              text: "<p>Pretty bad. I tried using Ubuntu on my Surface Laptop and gave up pretty much immediately. The problem is a lack of drivers. I couldn&#x27;t get the keyboard working and the device would never &quot;sleep&quot;, so I didn&#x27;t even try seeing if a pen would work. The touchscreen was functional.</p>",
