                                  author: "zeusk",
                                  title: null,
                                  url: null,
                                  text: "<p>I don&#x27;t see how it relates to Github but sure, link me to someplace I can read up on it because a Google search of &quot;Microsoft Linux patent racket&quot; only led me to an obvious troll bait blog.</p>",
