                                      author: "bitmapbrother",
                                      title: null,
                                      url: null,
                                      text: '<p>Microsoft milks Casio for using Linux:  \n<a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.theregister.co.uk&#x2F;2011&#x2F;09&#x2F;20&#x2F;signs_deal_with_casio_for_undisclosed_sum&#x2F;" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.theregister.co.uk&#x2F;2011&#x2F;09&#x2F;20&#x2F;signs_deal_with_cas...</a></p><p>And there are many more companies they&#x27;ve sued for using Linux.</p>',
