                                          type: "comment",
                                          author: "zeusk",
                                          title: null,
                                          url: null,
                                          text: "<p>I don&#x27;t want to sound dismissive but you&#x27;ve linked to a blog post from 2016, which in its entirety only mentions how much they make from the entire patent portfolio and a wild guess on how much they could be making from &quot;Linux patent racket&quot; and no other details on who they&#x27;re pursuing or what the demands are&#x2F;were.</p>",
