                              title: null,
                              url: null,
                              text: "<p>You are native to think they want to support open source. This is an American, capitalistic company who have crushed many opponents exactly the way they are doing now. Embrace, extend, extinguish. It&#x27;s their thing. You can Google it even.</p>",
