                                          type: "comment",
                                          author: "stuntkite",
                                          title: null,
                                          url: null,
                                          text: "<p>The first question I asked was really important. I think y&#x27;all are selling snake oil. Your responses here confirm that for me.</p><p>I personally will be avoiding your organization like the plague.</p>",
