                      author: "TACIXAT",
                      title: null,
                      url: null,
                      text: "<p>This was absolutely my first thought too. I&#x27;ve developed for work over the last year on Windows. It&#x27;s dark patterns to suck up data and ads now. There are ads on the login screen!</p>",
