                              created_at_i: 1528113807,
                              type: "comment",
                              author: "AnIdiotOnTheNet",
                              title: null,
                              url: null,
                              text: "<p>&gt; Also, in many years my amount of downtime due to Debian&#x27;s unattended-upgrades is exactly 0.</p><p>That&#x27;s nice for you, but if you use any non-open software or software not covered by the package repo then there&#x27;s a fairly good chance you&#x27;ll see downtime after an upgrade of your linux distro.</p>",
                              points: null,
