                                  author: "poooogles",
                                  title: null,
                                  url: null,
                                  text: "<p>&gt;You have pretty much misunderstood the entire point of open source software.</p><p>What? That&#x27;s a stretch of a comment from saying both the Ubuntu and Windows behaviour of updates is the same out of the box.</p>",
