                              url: null,
                              text: "<p>Companies that use github, both as teams on the main website and with the enterprise version, pay 9 dollars per month per user. If Microsoft can get it&#x27;s enterprise customers to trust the product enough to pay that sort of a price this will be a very profitable acquisition for Microsoft. If anything, I don&#x27;t think github would&#x27;ve ever been able to acquire enterprise customers had microsoft not made this acquisition.</p>",
