                                  created_at_i: 1528083250,
                                  type: "comment",
                                  author: "zer00eyz",
                                  title: null,
                                  url: null,
                                  text: "<p>I think I should have said sourceforge&#x2F;skype - I don&#x27;t think MS is going to detonate GitHub the same way sourceforge went.</p><p>But I also don&#x27;t have a lot of confidence in them doing well by the community either... it could be as &quot;harmless&quot; as a move to &quot;Microsoft logins&quot; that kills it off.</p>",
                                  points: null,
