                      created_at_i: 1528065449,
                      type: "comment",
                      author: "Silhouette",
                      title: null,
                      url: null,
                      text: "<p>Indeed. I&#x27;m always a little surprised at how readily developers recommend VS Code, given the lack of privacy guarantees and Microsoft&#x27;s recent track record on both telemetry and quietly overriding past user settings with updates.</p>",
                      points: null,
                      parent_id: 17222324,
