                                          text: "<p>&gt; Relatedly, Maps shows me when a location is likely to be popular vs unpopular. I have to assume that&#x27;s based on the location history of everyone using Maps</p><p>This is based on the location history of everyone using Android.  Its the Google Location Services requests going back and forth all the time that tells them where people go.</p>",
