          url: null,
          text: '<p>It makes that Gitlab graph <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;about.gitlab.com&#x2F;images&#x2F;blogimages&#x2F;forrester-ci-wave-graphic.png" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;about.gitlab.com&#x2F;images&#x2F;blogimages&#x2F;forrester-ci-wave...</a> even more interesting.</p>',
