                  created_at_i: 1528088059,
                  type: "comment",
                  author: "erikpukinskis",
                  title: null,
                  url: null,
                  text: "<p>Ya, they can’t do the same tricks they did before. You do have to wonder what new tricks they might pull though.</p><p>“I can’t hurt you now, I have these handcuffs on” doesn’t mean you can full trust someone who hit you.</p><p>(All that aside, I have notice what does appear to be real cultural change at MS)</p>",
