                  type: "comment",
                  author: "malkia",
                  title: null,
                  url: null,
                  text: "<p>AFAIK, I don&#x27;t think anyone seriously used VSS inside Microsoft, but heard that long time ago they forked perforce in customized way... A bit like google.</p>",
                  points: null,
