              text: "<p>Actually my real point was: scratch an itch and find you have lice living off you.  No, err that&#x27;s not it.</p><p>It is genuinely nice to see hard work pay off.  Github have seriously put their back into it to create an environment that a lot of people feel comfortable with.  I sincerely hope that MS do not fuck it up and wish them both all the best.</p><p>We still have git itself - that has never changed.  That is the power of open source software.</p>",
