      created_at_i: 1528058528,
      type: "comment",
      author: "gkya",
      title: null,
      url: null,
      text: "<p>I&#x27;m kind of happy with this happening as it seems to me that this can cause the VCS hosting arena to diversify a little bit.  The &quot;monopoly&quot; of github always worried me as a huge freaky single point of failure.</p>",
