              author: "gkya",
              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p>I don&#x27;t understand why a solo dev needs to host his private repos somewhere.  You can just keep it on your machine, and have it backed up with the rest of your data.  And given git is distributed, you should be able to work with teams w&#x2F;o requiring Github.</p>",
