              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p>Atom has a whole team under Github. If they&#x27;re both run by Microsoft, that seems like a clear cost-cutting measure; why develop two vastly similar electron-based code editors when you could just move that team + all of the interesting tech into VSCode?</p>",
