              created_at_i: 1528058889,
              type: "comment",
              author: "madeofpalk",
              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p>I use neither, and I can see that the two take fairly different approaches, but why would you say they&#x27;re build for different purposes. I don&#x27;t think it&#x27;s clear why a single org (though very far apart) has two approaches for a code text editor.</p>",
