              type: "comment",
              author: "carlosdp",
              title: null,
              url: null,
              text: "<p>What different purposes? They&#x27;re both text editors &#x2F; lightweight IDEs focusing on plugin extensibility built on top of Electron. They&#x27;re literally the same thing.</p>",
              points: null,
              parent_id: 17221585,
