      url: null,
      text: "<p>Microsoft being an owner here doesn&#x27;t bother me that much.</p><p>The Azure integrations are inevitable.  I guess we&#x27;ll see if Microsoft has learned that strong-armed vendor lock-in makes people not like them.  At this point, I am more glad they were acquired by Microsoft than Amazon.  Still - there is still so much Microsoft ill-will, that this will take away the aura of &#x27;software purity&#x27; from the GitHub.</p><p>Microsoft, please be a kind steward... I don&#x27;t want to waste time migrating.</p>",
