      text: "<p>The negativity in here is crazy. It‘s not even official yet everyone already seems to know that Microsoft will destroy Github. \nMicrosoft tried really hard to improve their relationship with developers in the last couple of years and they surely don‘t want to spend a lot of money just to destroy the relationship again. \nI can understand the scepticism and that people dislike the fact that Github is not independant anymore, but saying that Github will be ruined? We should be better than this.</p>",
