          author: "mythrwy",
          title: null,
          url: null,
          text: "<p>I hate when people accuse others of negativity when manifestly negative thing happen.</p><p>&quot;Hey, stop punching me in the face!&quot;</p><p>&quot;Why are you being negative?&quot;</p><p>There are very good reasons people aren&#x27;t happy about this. Microsoft&#x27;s track record for one. And the loss of independence of major repo source for another. Not being happy about this isn&#x27;t being &quot;negative&quot;. It&#x27;s entirely understandable.</p>",
