      created_at_i: 1528058931,
      type: "comment",
      author: "aphextron",
      title: null,
      url: null,
      text: "<p>What a betrayal. I&#x27;m starting to get really sick of this whole economic paradigm in general. A few lucky smart people who were in the right place at the right time become fabulously wealthy beyond the dreams of the greatest kings who ever lived in history, off the work and contributions of millions of users creating all of the content for free, with absolutely no say in anything. Is this really the best way to do things?</p>",
      points: null,
