                          text: "<p>Again: So? I think people focus too much on the &quot;VCs are getting rich&quot; part while overlooking &quot;the world is creating thousands of things that wouldn&#x27;t otherwise exist&quot; part.</p><p>If you imagine what the world would be like without any incentive to create, it would be a very different place.</p>",
