          title: null,
          url: null,
          text: "<p>Microsoft is big, with different divisions you can consider what it did with consumer apps, but you&#x27;d be better off considering what it has done with developer tools.</p><p>There, Microsoft shines.  So, we will just have to wait and see what they do.  My guess is the main thing they will do is make it super easy to deploy to azure from the github UI.</p>",
          points: null,
