          type: "comment",
          author: "mtgx",
          title: null,
          url: null,
          text: "<p>And just like they acquired Skype to please the NSA and make changes for its sake, I wonder if this is also a move to backdoor Github projects without the project owners and contributors noticing.</p><p>I, for one, would definitely stay away from any open source project that&#x27;s still hosted on a Microsoft-owned GitHub.</p>",
