                      created_at_i: 1528058643,
                      type: "comment",
                      author: "PascLeRasc",
                      title: null,
                      url: null,
                      text: "<p>Everyone says on here that VSCode is way faster than Atom but I&#x27;ve found the opposite every time I&#x27;ve tried, Atom opens faster and feels slicker when editing, especially multiline. I&#x27;m also not a fan of the VS UI and its icon.</p>",
