              text: "<p>I am expecting the owners of these sort of accounts to just move away. I am certainly not expecting MS to mess with the accounts in any way.</p><p>Another issue: \nLets say I am a small business competing with MS on some very small niche market. Lets say all my code is on a private github repository. \nWould I stay on GitHub for a moment after this news? I mean I know these are separate companies (Microsoft and GitHub), but I still will be moving away <i>right now</i>.</p>",
