      title: null,
      url: null,
      text: '<p>Why Github can&#x27;t host the Linux kernel community</p><p><a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;news.ycombinator.com&#x2F;item?id=14972872" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;news.ycombinator.com&#x2F;item?id=14972872</a></p>',
