                          author: "jayroh",
                          title: null,
                          url: null,
                          text: "<p>It&#x27;s a really bad look for the CEO of the company.</p><p>At it&#x27;s core what is a hashtag even? It&#x27;s means to amplify a &quot;thing&quot;. It&#x27;s a means to <i>make it</i> a thing.</p><p>That&#x27;s why it&#x27;s tasteless. It&#x27;s a shameless means to use the opportunity to ride the wave of the event instead of being classy, taking a back seat for a while, and handling the obvious influx resulting from this.</p>",
                          points: null,
