                          type: "comment",
                          author: "slg",
                          title: null,
                          url: null,
                          text: "<p>Sure, but it was more the manner of the promotion itself that was off-putting.  There was no substance to any of the comments saying why we should switch or why Gitlab isn&#x27;t going to follow the exact same path and be purchased by Google in 6 months.  Instead it was a gloating comment that came off like a vulture circling a sick animal.</p>",
