                          author: "matthewmacleod",
                          title: null,
                          url: null,
                          text: "<p>At a guess, I&#x27;d say a classy and less tasteless move would be a nice post giving their view on this rumour, pointing out the benefits of Gitlab, and giving some background on any efforts that might be needed to scale up. I&#x27;m sure it would quite quickly be pushed up to the top of the list and be a useful resource for people who might not have known about it or what it does.</p><p>A sloganeering hashtag is basically the opposite of that.</p>",
